params._factory: The factory that this deployer will be registered with.

deployHyperdrive(bytes32,string,(address.details: This can only be deployed by the associated factory.

params.__name: The name of the Hyperdrive pool.
params._deployConfig: The deploy configuration of the Hyperdrive pool.
params._extraData: The extra data that contains the pool and sweep targets.
params._salt: The create2 salt used to deploy Hyperdrive.

returns._0: The address of the newly deployed Hyperdrive instance.

deployTarget(bytes32,(address,address,ad.details: This can only be deployed by the associated factory.As a convention, target0 must be deployed first. After this, the      targets can be deployed in any order.

params._deployConfig: The deploy configuration of the Hyperdrive pool.
params._extraData: The extra data that contains the pool and sweep targets.
params._salt: The create2 salt used to deploy the target.
params._targetIndex: The index of the target to deploy.

returns.target: The address of the newly deployed target instance.

returns._0: numTargets The number of targets that need to be deployed for a         full deployment.

initialize(bytes32,address,uint256,uint2.details: This can only be deployed by the associated factory.This function utilizes several helper functions that provide      flexibility to implementations.

params._contribution: The amount of capital to supply. The units of this        quantity are either base or vault shares, depending on the value        of `_options.asBase`.
params._lp: The LP that is initializing the pool.
params._options: The options that configure how the initialization is        settled.

returns.lpShares: The initial number of LP shares created.

coreDeployer().notice: The contract used to deploy new instances of Hyperdrive.

deployHyperdrive(bytes32,string,(address.notice: Deploys a Hyperdrive instance with the given parameters.

deployTarget(bytes32,(address,address,ad.notice: Deploys a Hyperdrive target instance with the given parameters.

deployments(bytes32).notice: Gets the deployment specified by the deployment ID.

factory().notice: The factory that this deployer will be registered with.

getNumberOfTargets().notice: Gets the number of targets that need to be deployed for a full         deployment.

initialize(bytes32,address,uint256,uint2.notice: Initializes a pool that was deployed by this coordinator.

target0Deployer().notice: The contract used to deploy new instances of HyperdriveTarget0.

target1Deployer().notice: The contract used to deploy new instances of HyperdriveTarget1.

target2Deployer().notice: The contract used to deploy new instances of HyperdriveTarget2.

target3Deployer().notice: The contract used to deploy new instances of HyperdriveTarget3.

version().notice: Returns the deployer coordinator's version.The deployer coordinator's version.
